{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/fixing-broken-responsive-images-on-shopify","result":{"pageContext":{"id":250,"date":"2021-01-02T07:59:11","date_gmt":"2021-01-02T07:59:11","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=250"},"modified":"2021-07-21T08:23:12","modified_gmt":"2021-07-21T08:23:12","slug":"fixing-broken-responsive-images-on-shopify","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/fixing-broken-responsive-images-on-shopify/","title":{"rendered":"Fixing broken responsive images on Shopify"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>So, you just setup your theme. You add an &#8220;<em>image with text&#8221;<strong> </strong></em>section or any other section that is supposed to show an image, but when you take a look on mobile the edges are being cut off. <br><br>If you are going through this right now worry not, I&#8217;ll teach you a way to permanently fix this issue.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-downloading-the-section-file\">Downloading the section file </h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Download the files clicking <a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/responsive-banner-section-pro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-the-installation-process\">The installation process</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, go to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.</li><li>Under <strong>sections</strong> click on &#8220;Add a new section&#8221;.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"356\" height=\"793\" class=\"wp-image-257\" style=\"width: 300px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image.png\" alt=\"\"></li><li>Write the following: <strong>ezfy-responsive-banner</strong>.<strong> </strong><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"783\" height=\"271\" class=\"wp-image-259\" style=\"width: 400px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-1.png 783w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-1-600x208.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-1-768x266.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 783px) 100vw, 783px\" /></li><li>Click on the button <strong>create section</strong>.</li><li>Inside this new file, delete everything in it.</li><li>Copy the code that you have downloaded, either the free or pro version, paste it in and save.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1237\" height=\"754\" class=\"wp-image-261\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-2.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-2.png 1237w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-2-600x366.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-2-1200x731.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-2-768x468.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1237px) 100vw, 1237px\" /></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-adding-it-to-your-website-via-the-customize-panel\">Adding it to your website via the customize panel</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Click on <strong>customize theme</strong> at the top of the page.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1056\" height=\"352\" class=\"wp-image-263\" style=\"width: 400px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-3.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-3.png 1056w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-3-600x200.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-3-768x256.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1056px) 100vw, 1056px\" /></li><li>Find the option <strong>add section</strong>. You may need to scroll down if you have a lot of sections.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"381\" height=\"580\" class=\"wp-image-265\" style=\"width: 200px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-4.png\" alt=\"\"></li><li>Look for <strong>custom by EZFY</strong>. You&#8217;ll now see your section there. Click on it to add it to your theme.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"377\" height=\"436\" class=\"wp-image-267\" style=\"width: 300px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/image-5.png\" alt=\"\"></li><li>Now just customize it as per your wish and click on <strong>save </strong>once you&#8217;re done!<br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>If you need any further assistance we are here for you! Reach out to <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong> and we&#8217;ll be happy to help.</p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Learn how to fix images being cut off on mobile.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":253,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[154,12],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/broken-image-1-600x303.jpg","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/broken-image-1-100x100.jpg","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/broken-image-1-1200x607.jpg","post_count":2,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Code Tutorial","product"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/250"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=250"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/250/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1058,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/250/revisions/1058"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/253"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/m